{"tid":276178,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【Welcome To MongKok】過百球迷送別偉豪　Kim Sir爭啲變送禮金","createTime":"2017-06-08T15:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T01:38:32.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"687080807cbb9ca1fc478a94bad052f0ac706bfc","tid":276178,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/231242_76885488cb7965374dcb9919f6f13af9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F231242_76885488cb7965374dcb9919f6f13af9.jpg&h=9cc33412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際熱身賽香港主場出擊，最終同約旦打成0:0平手，呢場亦係陳偉豪嘅告別戰，賽後佢發出告別感言，更一度哽咽，場面感人。偉豪離開球場之時，有為數過百球迷維住偶像，要偉豪影相簽名留念，Fans們送禮物又送蛋糕，偉豪當然開心；有球迷問偉豪，可唔可以親自帶領南華再下一屆重返港超聯，偉豪亦爽快答應。<span style=\"color: red;\">之後仲發生一段小插曲，因為收球迷禮物應接不暇，因而放低港隊主教練金判坤較早前所送嘅大相禮物；之後離開時偉豪唔記得攞番，好彩有球迷提佢：「偉豪仲有呢樣呀，你唔好搞到Kim Sir做送禮金呀！」認真搞笑！ </span>"},{"pid":"80c66667d06c7d6c80998a98ed08dcddbfe2fa4e","tid":276178,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021a352af884ed3a999e13d35676324490198e0f","tid":276178,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T01:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}